I"p<p>I, Nathan Courtney, being a resident of the West Riding of Yorkshire declare:</p>

<ul>
  <li>That Yorkshire is three Ridings and the City of York, with these Boundaries of 1140 years standing.</li>
  <li>That the address of all places in these Ridings is Yorkshire</li>
  <li>That all persons born therein or resident therein and loyal to the Ridings are Yorkshiremen and women</li>
  <li>That any person or corporate body which deliberately ignores or denies the aforementioned shall forfeit all claim to Yorkshire status.</li>
</ul>

<p>These declarations made this Yorkshire Day 2015.</p>

<p>God Save the Queen!</p>
